{"tid":918033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣心怡幼稚園總監涉偷拍被捕　傳涉幼童如廁片段　至少50受害人","createTime":"2018-11-27T01:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T02:09:13.000Z","uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a20d90aa458fb845bea5ccd3e11cc3d5a6e5faf","tid":918033,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"有報道指，<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣心怡天地國際幼兒園暨幼稚園</span>麗城校園的馬姓男總監，上周五（23日）因涉嫌偷拍被捕，估計受害人數至少50人。<br />\n警方今晚（26日）回覆《香港01》查詢時證實消息，指於上周四（22日）下午接獲一名29歲女子報案，指懷疑一名36歲本地男子於洗手間內偷拍，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第十隊跟進。<br />\n警方於翌日（23日）在油麻地區一單位拘捕該名男子，涉嫌「有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦」，被捕男子已獲准保釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKVsbxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKVsbxU.png&h=511cc459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n班中產比四 五千甚至更多去呢d幼稚園 原來送仔女去比人偷拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891959f759a8994ab8d7470650b1c5f909fd20e3","tid":918033,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"38190475b0efede676d188b11386ecdd80d78cee","tid":918033,"uid":208159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ef8bf4abd50cd38c9b70fe4f52e0ed08e47f7cf","tid":918033,"uid":183219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:46:07.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"bcf1bf7d77036bacd08b60275fa3730ae68b53e7","tid":918033,"uid":2223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:08:27.000Z","msg":"對住變態戀童蘿莉控一定唔可以手軟！<br />\n切佢柒，爆佢丸"},{"pid":"c23a9448aab9cf5efbf95fcca925779598159a51","tid":918033,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"人渣，垃圾！"}]}